ath heat the dense clumps,\nwhich as a result expand and essentially dissolve in the ambient medium.\nTherefore, the star formation activity in DLAs is strongly regulated by the\nradiative feedback, both from the external UV background and internal stellar\nsources and we predict quiescent evolution of DLAs (not starburst-like\nevolution).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2005 20:01:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 May 2006 22:17:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
