al energies. We\nemphasize the simplicity of this effective field theory approach as compared to\nthe full quantum string computations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2005 19:37:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Sep 2005 03:18:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 14 Sep 2005 19:13:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 18 Sep 2005 21:45:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-17"}
